{"tid":2048451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑客組織「ANONYMOUS] 爆料 聲稱特朗普捲愛潑斯坦淫媒案","createTime":"2020-06-02T23:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T17:53:37.000Z","uid":188437,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"97fc1adecad9e9614244c3d55dd28ec46cc1b028","tid":2048451,"uid":188437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:40:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%8F-%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8D%B2%E6%84%9B%E6%BD%91%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E6%B7%AB%E5%AA%92%E6%A1%88-214500166.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B0%258F-%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2599-%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%258D%25B2%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25BD%2591%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259D%25A6%25E6%25B7%25AB%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%25A1%2588-214500166.html&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=60a25e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%8F-%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8D%B2%E6%84%9B%E6%BD%91%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E6%B7%AB%E5%AA%92%E6%A1%88-214500166.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】國際黑客組織「無名氏」近日在社交網公布一份法律文件，聲稱美國總統特朗普與已故「元首級淫媒」愛潑斯坦，曾強姦一名十三歲少女。無名氏亦聲稱，曾入侵明尼蘇達州警方的電腦系統，指過去二十年該州有一百九十三人死於警暴。<br />\n<br />\n稱過去20年 193人死於警暴<br />\n<br />\n無名氏公布名為「愛潑斯坦小黑書」（Jeffrey Epstein's Little Black Book，暫譯）的文件，披露一名女子曾稱十三歲時被特朗普及愛潑斯坦強姦。無名氏指控，特朗普命人殺害愛潑斯坦，掩飾販賣兒童和強姦的罪名。特朗普暫未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n無名氏亦提及黑人男子弗洛伊德死於警暴一案，指警暴和謀殺是美國普遍問題，當中以明尼蘇達州警方最惡名昭彰，弗洛伊德遇害只是冰山一角，眾多案件因無案發片段而湮沒。<br />\n<br />\n無名氏認為，所有涉事的警員都需要面對刑事起訴，當中跪頸殺死弗洛伊德的沙文應控以謀殺罪，並批評道︰「不幸地，我們不相信你們腐敗的組織能主持公義，所以我們要向世界揭露你們的眾多罪行。」"},{"pid":"62653d3c869b96ba5df7c50e2fa385776b6e2f42","tid":2048451,"uid":234089,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:43:03.000Z","msg":"共產黨統一了宇宙<br />\n<br />\nBoommmm<br />\n宇宙大爆炸"},{"pid":"819a467d830185643cc93d544d1e8f3983a00a4e","tid":2048451,"uid":188437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:46:30.000Z","msg":"又釣世班五毛打手出黎"},{"pid":"b846b0ff4ee4daf63f14c607ce2bffad61a8c414","tid":2048451,"uid":112784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"62653d3c869b96ba5df7c50e2fa385776b6e2f42","tid":2048451,"uid":234089,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:43:03.000Z","msg":"共產黨統一了宇宙<br />\n<br />\nBoommmm<br />\n宇宙大爆炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:50:24.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味，我唔想活係共產黨獨大嘅世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493959bed5463b8cbd3f36a9c577e29902ac3738","tid":2048451,"uid":72228,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:57:20.000Z","msg":"anonymous唔爆下共產黨料<br />\n共產黨仲多料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aa677f9c90be9590b721525a71edec947a78e9","tid":2048451,"uid":209890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:02:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d474b94e8d1d9c73cd689b154ef6d00ee2f4698","tid":2048451,"uid":188437,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"anonymous  撐香港架喎<br />\n轉頭成班唔岩聽又屈人奶共牙?"},{"pid":"d199f1da0bc0d30b323c659ee5f1502734c89467","tid":2048451,"uid":35776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"493959bed5463b8cbd3f36a9c577e29902ac3738","tid":2048451,"uid":72228,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T23:57:20.000Z","msg":"anonymous唔爆下共產黨料<br />\n共產黨仲多料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.g